son]] * [[Edward Israel]] * [[Hjalmar Johansen]] * [[Antony Jinman]] * [[Erling Kagge]] * [[Otto Kalvitsa]] * [[Elisha Kent Kane]] * [[Sydney L. Kirkby]] * [[Gerald Ketchum]] * [[Maria Klenova]] * [[Lauge Koch]] * [[Aleksandr Kolchak]] * [[Nikolai Kolomeitsev]] * [[Alexander Kuchin]] * [[Paul Landry]] * [[Dmitry Laptev]] * [[Khariton Laptev]] * [[Christian Leden]] * [[Ernest de Koven Leffingwell]] * [[Percy Lemon]] * [[Godske Lindenov]] * [[Sir Martin Lindsay, 1st Baronet|Martin Lindsay]] * [[Fyodor Litke]] * [[Ivan Lyakhov]] * [[Alistair Mackay]] * [[Alexander Mackenzie (explorer)|Alexander MacKenzie]] * [[Cecil Madigan]] * [[Rune Malterud]] * [[Stepan Malygin]] * [[Donal T. Manahan]] * [[Albert Hastings Markham]] * [[Eric Marshall]] * [[Fyodor Matisen]] * [[Fyodor Matyushkin]] * [[Douglas Mawson]] * [[Francis Leopold McClintock]] * [[Jim McNeill]] * [[Janice Meek]] * [[Alexander Middendorf]] * [[Ejnar Mikkelsen]] * [[Fyodor Minin]] * [[Gerhard Friedrich Müller|Gerhard Muller]] * [[Fridtjof Nansen]] * [[George Nares]] * [[Alfred Gabriel Nathorst]] * [[Edward W Nelson]] * [[Umberto Nobile]] * [[Adolf Erik Nordenskiöld]] * [[Børge Ousland]] * [[Dmitry Ovtsyn]] * [[Pyotr Pakhtusov]] * [[Nathaniel Palmer]] * [[Ivan Papanin]] * [[William Parry (explorer)|William Parry]] * [[Charlie Paton]] * [[Robert Edwin Peary]] * [[Yakov Permyakov]] * [[Eric Philips]] * [[Ralph Plaisted]] * [[Fedot Popov]] * [[Richard Profit]] * [[Vasili Pronchishchev]] * [[Maria Pronchishcheva]] * [[Lewis Gordon Pugh]] * [[Emil Racovita]] * [[Pierre-Esprit Radisson]] * [[John Rae (explorer)|John Rae]] * [[Knud Rasmussen]] * [[Andrew Regan]] * [[George W. Rice (photographer)|George W. Rice]] * [[John Richardson (naturalist)|John Richardson]] * [[Hjalmar Riiser-Larsen]] * [[Quintin Riley]] * [[Alfred Ritscher]] * [[Edith Ronne]] * [[Finn Ronne]] * [[James Clark Ross]] * [[John Ross (Arctic explorer)|John Ross]] * [[Vladimir Rusanov]] * [[John Rymill]] * [[Rudolf Samoylovich]] * [[Yakov Sannikov]] * [[